metadata.name: There was a silence
metadata.description:
Zhang Yuanqing put the black card into the pocket of the charging clothes, while picking up the mobile phone to send a message to the soldier brother:



"Which club is the supreme card, at least give me the address or contact information."



I left that message, and I haven't heard back in half an hour.



Zhang Yuanqing simply dialed the phone of Bing brother.



After two "beeps", the call was connected, and the man's deep voice came through the speaker:



"Feed! I am Lei Yibing's father."



"Uncle Ray? Zhang Yuanqing said joyfully:



"Soldier Brother back to Songhai this week? Put him on the phone. I need to speak to him."



There was a silence on the other side of the line, and then a deep, painful voice:



"Yuanzi, I am in Jiangnan province. Ah Bing he is missing......."



Soldier brother is missing? ! Zhang Yuanqing stayed on the spot, separated a few seconds, and vacant and eager to ask:



'What's the matter?
